title: Ep. - 371 - BRITNEY SPEARS CONSERVATORSHIP REAL HOUSEWIVES OF NEW YORK RECAP
description:
Attorney Scott Rahn discusses the latest update to the Britney Spears conservatorship. Last week Britney Spears addressed a court for the first known time in more than two years following the increased interest in her conservatorship after the release of The New York Times' "Framing Britney Spears" documentary and the #FreeBritney movement organized by her fans. Scott is Founder and Managing Partner of RMO LLP, 

 

Podcast host Taria Faison reviews this week’s episode of Real Housewives of New York. Taria is host of What Else is Going On podcast.
